si.JDEXi

Class Value

  • java.lang.Object
    • si.JDEXi.Value

  • public class Value
extends java.lang.Object
    Value class. Represents a single (non-distributed) value that can be assigned to an attribute. Contains elements:
    • String name: value name
    • Integer ordinal: corresponding ordinal value
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Andrej Kogovšek, Dušan Omerèeviæ, Marko Bohanec
